android.media
Interface AudioTrack.OnPeriodicNotificationListener

Enclosing class:
AudioTrack
public static interface AudioTrack.OnPeriodicNotificationListener

Interface definition for a callback to be invoked for each periodic AudioTrack update during playback. The update interval is set by setPositionNotificationPeriod().

Method Summary
 void onPeriodicNotification(AudioTrack track)
          Called on the listener to periodically notify it that the playback head has reached a multiple of the notification period.
